---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---
<Layout title="Services | Salerno Trucking" description="Mixer truck fleet capacity solutions for ready-mix producers and dependable concrete delivery for placement contractors.">
  <PageHero eyebrow="Our Services" title="Flexible Capacity. Dependable Delivery." text="Solutions designed around the real operating needs of ready-mix producers and concrete placement contractors." />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container service-detail-grid">
      <article class="service-detail reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">For Ready-Mix Producers</p>
        <h2>Fleet Capacity Solutions</h2>
        <p class="lead">Increase production without sacrificing customer service or professional representation.</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>Mixer truck and operator support</li>
          <li>Long-term fleet capacity</li>
          <li>Seasonal and peak-demand support</li>
          <li>Experienced professional operators</li>
          <li>Reliable equipment</li>
          <li>Nationwide project experience</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Our trucks and operators integrate into your operation as an extension of your team. We help protect customer relationships, meet delivery commitments, and support growth targets.</p>
        <a class="button" href="/partner-with-us">Discuss Fleet Capacity</a>
      </article>

      <article class="service-detail dark-card reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">For Placement Contractors</p>
        <h2>Concrete Delivery</h2>
        <p class="lead">Straightforward service from material sourcing through placement.</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>Concrete delivery to your jobsite</li>
          <li>Material sourcing through trusted producers</li>
          <li>Transparent pricing</li>
          <li>No standing time charges</li>
          <li>Reliable scheduling</li>
          <li>Professional communication</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We coordinate the moving parts so your crew can focus on placement. You receive clear expectations, dependable scheduling, and professional communication throughout the process.</p>
        <a class="button button-light" href="/partner-with-us">Request Delivery</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-muted">
    <div class="container narrow centered reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Standard</p>
      <h2>We Treat Every Delivery Like Our Reputation Is Riding on It.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Because it is—and so is yours.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
